OL,3,CBobby Singleton appointed PSNI deputy
OL,4,Cchief constable
OL,6,FBobby Singleton has been named as the
OL,7,FPSNI's new deputy chief constable.
OL,9,FHe replaces Mark Hamilton in the role,
OL,10,Fafter he announced his retirement in
OL,11,FSeptember.
OL,13,FWelcoming the appointment, Chief
OL,14,FConstable Jon Boutcher said: "This is
OL,15,Fgreat news for the PSNI.
OL,17,F"Bobby is dedicated to policing in
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland and he brings a
OL,19,Fwealth of knowledge, skill, leadership
OL,20,Fand experience to the job.
