OL,3,CBobby Singleton appointed PSNI deputy
OL,4,Cchief constable
OL,6,FBobby Singleton joined the PSNI as one
OL,7,Fof the first student officers in
OL,8,FNovember 2001 and over the past 23
OL,9,Fyears he has held a number of roles
OL,10,Fwithin the police service.
OL,12,FBetween 2014 and 2016 as a
OL,13,Fsuperintendent he was responsible for
OL,14,Fleading the delivery of community
OL,15,Fpolicing services for the city of
OL,16,FBelfast and as a firearms and public
OL,17,Forder commander a series of complex
OL,18,Fand challenging multi-agency
OL,19,Foperations.
