OL,3,CBobby Singleton appointed PSNI deputy
OL,4,Cchief constable
OL,6,FFrom April 2016 to May 2019, then a
OL,7,Fdetective superintendent, he was the
OL,8,Fservice's lead for drugs, Organised
OL,9,FCrime and the then newly established
OL,10,F'Paramilitary Crime Task Force' with
OL,11,Fthe National Crime Agency and Her
OL,12,FMajesty's Revenue and Customs.
OL,14,FOn promotion to detective chief
OL,15,Fsuperintendent he was appointed as
OL,16,Fhead of the PSNI's Legacy
OL,17,FInvestigation Branch in May 2019.
