OL,3,CBobby Singleton appointed PSNI deputy
OL,4,Cchief constable
OL,6,FIn March 2021 he was appointed
OL,7,Ftemporary assistant chief constable
OL,8,Fand head of the Community Safety
OL,9,FDepartment responsible for public
OL,10,Fprotection, crime prevention, criminal
OL,11,Fjustice and custody matters.
OL,13,FIn December 2021 he graduated from the
OL,14,FStrategic Command Course before being
OL,15,Fsubstantively appointed to Assistant
OL,16,FChief Constable by the Northern
OL,17,FIreland Policing Board in January 2022.
